706613f-a.title: Brooklyn: Sands Street - Jay Street
706613f-a.text:
Sands Street, north side, east from the Manhattan Bridge, over Jay
Street. Also seen is Bridge Street, east side, south from Sands Street.
November 1, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
